e asymptotic formulas connected by a switching function. Exemplary\ncalculations show that this new form of f(r12) performs somewhat better than\nthe correlation factors used thus far in the standard R12 or F12 theories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2013 20:41:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Sep 2013 18:03:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-10"}
