l cross-section of such structures is approximately circular. Results\nbased on isothermal models can be applied locally to polytropic layers. For\nvertical fields, magnetic flux concentrations of super-equipartition strengths\nform, which supports suggestions that sunspot formation might be a shallow\nphenomenon.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jul 2013 14:01:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Oct 2013 11:45:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 19 Dec 2013 19:10:23 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2014 09:46:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-27"}
