l protocols that would\nprobe these universal transitions between the normal gas, the superfluid gas,\nand the superfluid Efimov liquid.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jul 2013 15:59:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Aug 2013 10:06:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-06"}
